      "content": "okay thanks. i get the part about the speed of light thing now. but i'm still having a hard time wrapping my head around the \"why\" of it. like, what exactly is happening in that moment when the measurement happens? is there anything else scientists call this phenomenon, or is there a specific way people describe the weirdness of it?",
